search_workflow.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?countries ?countriesName WHERE { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q2462658; wdt:P27 wd:Q183. ?company wdt:P1037 ?person; wdt:P17 ?countries. ?countries <http://schema.org/name> ?countriesName. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?person wdt:P20 ?placeOfDeath}. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?company wdt:P17 wd:Q183}. } ORDER BY ?oName

ASK WHERE { SELECT DISTINCT ?personName WHERE { { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q2462658; wdt:P27 wd:Q183. ?company wdt:P1037 ?person; wdt:P17 ?countries. } UNION { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q2462658; wdt:P27 wd:Q183. ?company wdt:P169 ?person; wdt:P17 ?countries. } ?company <http://schema.org/name> ?companyName. ?person <http://schema.org/name> ?personName. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?person wdt:P20 ?placeOfDeath}. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?company wdt:P17 wd:Q183}. } }

search_workflow.narrative: return the people and the number of companies that they are related to
search_workflow.query: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?personName) AS ?howmany) WHERE { { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q2462658; wdt:P27 wd:Q183. ?company wdt:P1037 ?person; wdt:P17 ?countries. } UNION { ?person wdt:P106 wd:Q2462658; wdt:P27 wd:Q183. ?company wdt:P169 ?person; wdt:P17 ?countries. } ?company <http://schema.org/name> ?companyName. ?person <http://schema.org/name> ?personName. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?person wdt:P20 ?placeOfDeath}. FILTER NOT EXISTS{?company wdt:P17 wd:Q183}. } ORDER BY DESC (?howmany)
